{"case_id": "case-002-d4-04", "container": "D", "pipeline_depth": 4, "message": "Type 2 DM, eGFR 55, scheduled for CT with IV contrast tomorrow. On metformin 1000mg BID.", "latency_ms": 3244, "llm_calls": 1, "tokens_in": 182, "tokens_out": 101, "cost_usd": 8.79e-05, "task_success": true, "abstained": false, "answer": "Given the patient's eGFR of 55 mL/min/1.73m^2 (CKD G3a) and scheduled IV contrast administration, Metformin should be held prior to or at the time of contrast administration and for 48 hours following the procedure. Metformin should be re-initiated only after renal function has been re-evaluated and confirmed to be stable or improved, due to the increased risk of lactic acidosis in patients with impaired renal function receiving IV contrast.", "tool_calls": 0, "hop_metrics": [{"hop": "vector_ingress", "latency_ms": 6, "llm_calls": 0, "tokens_in": 0, "tokens_out": 0, "tool_calls": 0}, {"hop": "cache_gate", "latency_ms": 1, "llm_calls": 0, "tokens_in": 0, "tokens_out": 0, "tool_calls": 0}, {"hop": "writer", "latency_ms": 3232, "llm_calls": 1, "tokens_in": 182, "tokens_out": 101, "tool_calls": 0}], "embed_count": 1, "cache_hit": true, "cache_score": 0.9996996521949768, "variant": "exact_repeat", "error": null}
{"case_id": "case-002-d6-05", "container": "D", "pipeline_depth": 6, "message": "Type 2 DM, eGFR 55, scheduled for CT with IV contrast tomorrow. On metformin 1000mg BID.", "latency_ms": 4812, "llm_calls": 1, "tokens_in": 182, "tokens_out": 72, "cost_usd": 7.05e-05, "task_success": true, "abstained": false, "answer": "For a patient with an eGFR of 55 mL/min/1.73m^2, Metformin generally does not need to be withheld before or after intravenous contrast administration. However, it is prudent to monitor renal function post-procedure, particularly if other risk factors for acute kidney injury are present. (ACR Manual on Contrast Media)", "tool_calls": 0, "hop_metrics": [{"hop": "vector_ingress", "latency_ms": 6, "llm_calls": 0, "tokens_in": 0, "tokens_out": 0, "tool_calls": 0}, {"hop": "cache_gate", "latency_ms": 0, "llm_calls": 0, "tokens_in": 0, "tokens_out": 0, "tool_calls": 0}, {"hop": "writer", "latency_ms": 4801, "llm_calls": 1, "tokens_in": 182, "tokens_out": 72, "tool_calls": 0}], "embed_count": 1, "cache_hit": true, "cache_score": 0.9995256662368774, "variant": "exact_repeat", "error": null}
